column5: Went last evening and went 2 for 5. Landed 1 Coho (2-3lbs) and 1 Laker (4-5lbs). 55 to 65 FOW.
Nice pic! Did great out there...thanks for the report!
Thanks guys, he's on the smoker (with a couple small salmon) as we speak.
Beauty laker, Patches.  I bet the smoker does a great job.
Mmmm, smoked trout is a beautiful thing...  Mike
